300
00:16:26.353 --> 00:16:29.354
(speaking Spanish)

301
00:16:34.160 --> 00:16:36.194
Where are you from?

302
00:16:36.196 --> 00:16:38.029
I'm from Mexico.

303
00:16:38.031 --> 00:16:39.630
