304
00:16:39.632 --> 00:16:42.266
-Who do you work for?
-(speaking Spanish)

305
00:16:42.268 --> 00:16:44.435
Say
it!

306
00:16:44.437 --> 00:16:48.272
(speaking
Spanish)

307
00:16:48.274 --> 00:16:49.874
