a few days ago looking for work.

309
00:16:51.644 --> 00:16:53.644
-Bullshit!
-(grunts)

310
00:16:53.646 --> 00:16:57.448
You're working
for Camila
Vargas!

311
00:16:57.450 --> 00:16:58.983
(speaking Spanish)

312
00:16:58.985 --> 00:17:00.651
-And I know it.
-(speaking Spanish)

313
00:17:00.653 --> 00:17:02.620
