325
00:17:37.557 --> 00:17:38.856
(speaking Spanish)

326
00:17:38.858 --> 00:17:45.396
<i> ♪ ♪</i>

327
00:17:45.398 --> 00:17:49.734
CAMILA:
Can you hear me. Teresa?

328
00:17:49.736 --> 00:17:53.037
Get out of the van.

329
00:17:53.039 --> 00:17:54.038
