344
00:19:40.713 --> 00:19:43.147
I told you. be careful.

345
00:19:43.149 --> 00:19:45.550
Now you know what I mean.

346
00:19:45.552 --> 00:19:48.286
The last time
I'm gonna talk about this.

347
00:19:48.288 --> 00:19:51.289
