361
00:20:50.617 --> 00:20:52.550
If he sees your face.
he knows you.

362
00:20:52.552 --> 00:20:54.518
She knows you know him.
See how that works?

363
00:20:54.520 --> 00:20:56.687
If I know too
much.
I'm indispensable.

364
00:20:56.689 --> 00:21:00.358
If I know too little.
I'm
disposable.

365
00:21:02.895 --> 00:21:05.263
Did you listen
to a word I said?

366
00:21:05.265 --> 00:21:12.270
