367
00:21:22.815 --> 00:21:24.782
Lopez.

368
00:21:26.085 --> 00:21:27.485
Who's she?

369
00:21:27.487 --> 00:21:31.055
She's new.
She's running with me.

370
00:21:31.057 --> 00:21:33.124
