371
00:21:33.126 --> 00:21:35.760
I like faces I know.

372
00:21:35.762 --> 00:21:37.828
Where's Aveline?

373
00:21:37.830 --> 00:21:39.830
She
O.D.'d.

374
00:21:42.502 --> 00:21:44.302
Shame.

375
00:21:44.304 --> 00:21:47.071
I don't like this.

376
00:21:47.073 --> 00:21:49.774
Look. if you have a problem.
take it up with
Camila.

377
00:21:49.776 --> 00:21:51.609
I can sell this load
someplace
else.

378
00:21:51.611 --> 00:21:57.848
