mother.

398
00:23:02.081 --> 00:23:03.381
She's
sick.
She's got cancer.

399
00:23:03.383 --> 00:23:05.149
She's not long
for this
world.

400
00:23:05.151 --> 00:23:07.418
They're looking to get
out.
move back to
Cincinnati

401
00:23:07.420 --> 00:23:08.853
