403
00:23:11.190 --> 00:23:15.092
Yeah.
I like to dig.

404
00:23:15.094 --> 00:23:17.995
I can see that.

405
00:23:17.997 --> 00:23:19.597
However...

406
00:23:19.599 --> 00:23:22.266
