shipping.

410
00:23:30.243 --> 00:23:32.009
and it's not
swordfish.

411
00:23:32.011 --> 00:23:33.744
You neglected
to tell me that.

412
00:23:33.746 --> 00:23:35.446
Because it's not relevant.

413
00:23:35.448 --> 00:23:38.182
Ah. when you said you wanted
to keep this from your husband

414
00:23:38.184 --> 00:23:39.683
