415
00:23:39.685 --> 00:23:41.218
Not because you're trying
to
hide

416
00:23:41.220 --> 00:23:43.888
a little something
off the books for
yourself.

417
00:23:43.890 --> 00:23:45.589
I never said
I was trying to hide

418
00:23:45.591 --> 00:23:47.291
a little something
off the books.

419
00:23:47.293 --> 00:23:49.593
Yes. but you led me to believe
that that was the
case.

420
00:23:49.595 --> 00:23:52.363
You have a history
