buy his company too.

437
00:24:25.398 --> 00:24:28.799
Guess whose boats
were violating the rules.

438
00:24:28.801 --> 00:24:32.837
Everything my husband has.
I helped him build.

439
00:24:32.839 --> 00:24:34.672
So if you're afraid of him.

440
00:24:34.674 --> 00:24:38.843
