of me too.

441
00:24:38.845 --> 00:24:41.979
He won't know what happened
until it's too late.

442
00:24:41.981 --> 00:24:44.448
I need boats for shipping.

443
00:24:44.450 --> 00:24:47.651
And all you need to know is
that I'm fortifying my business

444
00:24:47.653 --> 00:24:50.187
