450
00:25:03.002 --> 00:25:04.835
That's what you said?

451
00:25:04.837 --> 00:25:06.136
For your loyalty.

452
00:25:06.138 --> 00:25:08.873
I'm willing to give you
a piece of...

453
00:25:08.875 --> 00:25:11.509
